Package: rgeospatialshiny
Title: R Geospatial Shiny App for Interactive Spatial Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Gabriel", "Demetrios Lafis", email = "gabriel.lafis@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An interactive Shiny application for geospatial data analysis and visualization.
    The package provides tools for loading, processing, analyzing, and visualizing spatial data
    with a focus on interactive maps, spatial statistics, and geoprocessing operations.
    Features include choropleth maps, point pattern analysis, spatial autocorrelation,
    and custom spatial queries through an intuitive user interface.
